metadata.name: Fear
metadata.description:
FEAR
Sainte Vie's first NFT release.
This animation is linked to Sainte Vie's first single "Fear" from his upcoming "Hypnotic Places" EP.

This NFT is a 1/1 collectible piece including:
- Lifetime guest list (+1)
- Meet and greet
- Fear T-shirt + hat

Artwork: Stillman X Yonson
Music: Sainte Vie
